《[[嗜血法医|嗜血法医]]》是[[美国|美国]]付费有线电视频道[[Showtime频道|Showtime]]旗下的[[电视连续剧|电视连续剧]]，改编自杰夫·林赛的小说《暗夜噩梦戴克斯特》。嗜血法医从2006年10月1日起首播<ref>{{cite web |url=http://media.www.washburnreview.org/media/storage/paper1140/news/2008/09/29/Entertainment/dexter.Book.Series.Similar.To.Tv-3458389.shtml |title=''Dexter'' book series similar to TV |accessdate=2009-01-16 |author=Ward, Kendra |date=2008-09-29 |work=The Review |publisher=Washburn University |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091005044534/http://media.www.washburnreview.org/media/storage/paper1140/news/2008/09/29/Entertainment/dexter.Book.Series.Similar.To.Tv-3458389.shtml |archivedate=2009-10-05 }}</ref>，电视剧以主角德克斯特·摩根的视角讲述了一个连环杀手的故事。德克斯特·摩根幼时目睹母亲被谋杀，造成永久性的心灵创伤，令到他长大后有杀人倾向。他当警察的养父哈利·摩根发现后，决定训练德克斯特只杀那些穷凶极恶的人，好为社会除害。哈利亦教晓德克斯特怎样消灭证据，让他不会被警方拘捕，而德克斯特最后则进入[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]大都会警局工作，成为他们重案组的血迹奔溅分析师<ref name="IGNs2">{{cite web |url=http://au.tv.ign.com/articles/771/771668p1.html |title=Paley Fest: ''Dexter'' |accessdate=2009-01-16 |date=2007-03-08 |publisher=IGN |first=Eric |last=Goldman |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130103051724/http://www.ign.com/articles/2007/03/08/paley-fest-dexter |archivedate=2013-01-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

该系列电视剧受到了评论家的普遍好评<ref name=metacritic>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/shows/dexter |title=''Dexter'' (Series: Showtime, Sunday 10:00p (60 minutes)) |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2009-08-14 |archive-date=2012-03-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/664mXuzuK?url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/dexter/season-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，首播当日便吸引了超过一百万观众<ref name=metacritic>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/tv/shows/dexter |title=''Dexter'' (Series: Showtime, Sunday 10:00p (60 minutes)) |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2009-08-14}}</ref>，是Showtime频道近年来收视率最高的电视剧<ref name="pilotratings">{{cite news|url=http://www.tvguide.com/news/Short-Cuts-Dexter-15508.aspx|title=Short Cuts: Dexter Slays the Ratings, and More!|work=TV Guide|author=Mitovich, Matt|date=2006-10-04|accessdate=2009-01-16|archive-date=2014-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140607081406/http://www.tvguide.com/news/Short-Cuts-Dexter-15508.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同时，也获得了包括[[卫星奖|卫星奖]]、[[金球奖|金球奖]]、[[美国电影学会|AFI奖]]、[[美國演員工會獎|SAG]]奖在内的多项奖项<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.producersguild.org/2009/01/05/2009-nominees-announced/ |title=Producers Guild of America » Blog Archive » 2009 Nominees Announced! |publisher=Producers Guild of America |date=2009-01-05|author=Rae  |accessdate=2009-08-14}} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/04/mad-men-project.html |title=The Watcher: ''Mad Men'', ''Project Runway'', ''Dexter'' honored with Peabodys |work=Chicago Tribune |date=2008-04-02 |author=Tempo |accessdate=2009-08-14 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201043719/http://featuresblogs.chicagotribune.com/entertainment_tv/2008/04/mad-men-project.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。此列表则收录了从2006年10月1日起播出的嗜血法医各集。2013年9月22日，《嗜血法医》宣布完結，共播出八季。

